</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px">
<div style="width: 155px">
<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px;">
<div style="margin:15px auto;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Hilye-i_Serif_6.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/Hilye-i_Serif_6.jpg/88px-Hilye-i_Serif_6.jpg" width="88" height="120" /></a></div>
